AN ACT SUPPORTING "LEARN AND EARN" INTERNSHIP
OPPORTUNITIES.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 Section 1. (NEW) (Effective July 1, 2026) (a) As used in this section,
2 "small business" means a business entity in the state that has fifty or
3 fewer employees.
4 (b) The Board of Trustees of The University of Connecticut and the
5 Board of Regents for Higher Education shall each, within the availability
